snippet.title: ManHunt Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait is Finally Over...

MANHUNT IS NOW AVAILABLE 

Features:

Cutscenes: 

Faster Cutscenes
Faster Moons
Faster Life-Up
Faster Cap Kingdom Wire
No Odyssey Cutscenes

___________________________________________


Healing System Revamped:

Checkpoints - 3
Hearts - 2
Moons - 1

___________________________________________

Runner | Hunter Features:

Runner:
Cappy Deals 1 Damage if he touches the opponent
6 Health
Gets Bubbled if he touches Lava/Poison/Void
Safezone

Hunter:
Cappy Deals 1 Damage if he touches the opponent
Compass pointing to the Runner


Thanks to Hesmakka who have done the mod with me !

Gamebanana: https://gamebanana.com/mods/536910
Github: NOT AVAILABLE
